Interface ITaxonomyInfoConfigurator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ITaxonomyInfoConfigurator
    This interface defines the objects in charge of initializing a taxonomy to be used by any IC-based semantic measure. All the semantic measures use the IC-node and edge-weights stored in the fields of the vertexes or edges. Therefore, any object that implements this interface can set these values to control the operation of any dependent measure.
